    <exercise xml:id="practice-5-2-4" label="P5-2-4">
      <title>Two-sample <m>z</m>-test Comparison</title>
      <statement>
        <p>Use technology to calculate a two-sample <m>z</m>-test for these data. How does the (two-sided) p-value compare to what you found in Checkpoint 5.2.c?</p>
      </statement>
